solution_code: public class Solution {--newline--    public int numTrees(int n) {--newline--        int [] G = new int[n+1];--newline--        G[0] = G[1] = 1;--newline--        --newline--        for(int i=2; i<=n; ++i) {--newline--            for(int j=1; j<=i; ++j) {--newline--                G[i] += G[j-1] * G[i-j];--newline--            }--newline--        }--newline--    --newline--        return G[n];--newline--    }--newline--}
